      "id": "/page/0/TextInlineMath/5",
      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">the tail of the <math display=\"inline\">n</math>-fold convolution of <math display=\"inline\">F</math>. We then say that F (or X) is subexponential (written <math display=\"inline\">F \\in \\mathcal{S}</math>) if one of the following equivalent conditions holds:</p>",
