      "block_type": "Equation",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Equation\">(a) <math display=\"block\">\\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{F^{n*}(x)}{\\overline{F}(x)} = n</math> for some (all) <math>n \\ge 2</math> and</p>",
