      "id": "/page/0/TextInlineMath/8",
      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">The heavy-tailedness of <math display=\"inline\">F \\in \\mathcal{S}</math> is demonstrated by the implications</p>",
