      "block_type": "Equation",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Equation\"><math display=\"block\">\\frac{\\overline{F^{2*}}(x)}{\\overline{F}(x)} = 2 \\int_0^{x/2} \\frac{\\overline{F}(x-y)}{\\overline{F}(x)} dF(y)</math><math display=\"block\">+ \\frac{(\\overline{F}(x/2))^2}{\\overline{F}(x)}, \\quad x &gt; 0 \\tag{6}</math></p>",
